Frank J. Coleman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_J._Coleman 0 Frank John Coleman (26 April 1888 – 29 November 1948) was an American silent film actor.Frank John Coleman was born on 26 April 1888 in Newburgh, New York.Coleman acted with Charlie Chaplin at Essanay Studios in Los Angeles, and continued with him at Mutual in June 1917.
